items.title: Three Americans killed by IS gunman in Syria, US military says
items.description: Two US soldiers and a civilian interpreter were killed in the attack, according to the US Central Command.

items.title: Belarus frees 123 prisoners as US lifts sanctions
items.description: Opposition activist Maria Kolesnikova is among those released in exchange for a deal with the US.

items.title: Angry fans throw chairs and bottles at Messi event in India
items.description: The Inter Miami and Argentina forward is in India for a tour, taking in events in Kolkata, Hyderabad, Mumbai and Delhi.

items.title: BBC captures celebrations as Belarus frees political prisoners
items.description: Southern & Eastern Europe correspondent Sarah Rainsford reports from Lithuania, where some of the released prisoners were taken.

items.title: Israel targets senior Hamas official in deadly Gaza strike
items.description: The strike killed Raed Saad, a senior commander in Hamas' Qassam Brigades, the Israeli military said.
